column3: For the years ended June 30, 2019 ("fiscal 2019"), June 30, 2018 ("fiscal 2018"), and June 30, 2017 ("fiscal 2017"), Professional Employer Organization ("PEO") revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $42,688.8 million, $39,140.9 million, and $34,567.4 million, respectively.
